summary: Beyond The Wall, AKA Game of Thrones S7E6, has been critically derided as the worst. episode. Ever. and I honestly do not...
body:
I Love This Episode

Beyond The Wall, AKA Game of Thrones S7E6, has been critically derided as the worst. episode. Ever. and I honestly do not understand it. There are so many gold moments: the Tormund and the Hound comedy road show, Jorah giving Jon the wink wink nudge nudge yeah I know you’re gonna impregnate my Khaleesi so just keep the damn sword, Daenerys being done with Tyrion’s bad advice, the prelude to Boat Sex (boat hand holding, heart eyes, and knee bending)…..so who honestly gives a fuck about inconsistent travel times, like the GOT fandom is Google Maps or something? There is a zombie polar bear, for Chrissakes!!!!


But there are so many jewels in this scene in particular:

0:10 - Jon’s like, Yeah Imma just get out of the way here

0:28 - all the boys just standing around dumbfounded like, Are we supposed to do something? Because all we can do is look at these fucking dragons blowing everything up

0:42 - heeerrrrrrreeeee’s DANY!

0:58 - Get out the way motherfucker that’s my woman

1:02 - I’m a little bit hard right now, is that inappropriate? Because she is a GODDESS and I’m just a dumb bastard who does stupid shit

1:10 - Come with me if you want to live!

1:14 - Jon Snow, why do you always have to be the hero?

2:25 - Jon and Rhaegal are both like, Tha Fuck just happened?

2:33 - can we appreciate how Rhaegal straight up peaces out on the whole operation? Like, fuck this shit, I’m out. You coming, Jon?

2:49 - All the boys like, Oh, that’s fucked up! Like, look how sad Tormund is!

3:14 - very angry Jon, staring down NK like, you killed mah boo’s dragon. You’re gonna die, motherfucker.

3:22 - but not today maybe

3:34 - ok yes I’m in love with this dumb motherfucker.

3:42 Hey Night King?

3:49 - Drogon’s wings knocking over all those wights - great detail

4:00 - Turns our Jorah can’t ride the dragon after all.

4:11 - Sorry Jon, I really am


And we don’t really see it but I imagine all the boys are like Holy Shit I’m flying on a dragon right now.


Spectacular scene! I love it!
